notFound.title: Karaa kee dhabdee?
notFound.description: Fuulli ati barbaaddu hin jiru, socho'ee, ykn URL irratti dogoggorri jira. Gara karaa keetti si deebisna.
notFound.hint: URL irratti dogoggora ilaali, ykn qajeelfama fayyadami.

errorBoundary.title: Wanti tokko sirrii hin deemne
errorBoundary.description: Gugurroon paaspoortii keenyaa dhimmicha irratti hojjechaa jiru. Haaromsi ykn gara manaatti deebi'i.
